  |= Tier |= Modelo |= Tareas |
  | OPUS (Critico) | claude-opus-4-6 | gaps, vcr, tests |
  | SONNET (Estandar) | claude-sonnet-4-5 | bugs, templates, data |
  | GEMINI (Vision) | gemini-2.5-pro | screenshots, UI |
